section.def:
Corporation
                                (公司) means the International
                        Finance Corporation;

paragraph.content:
Enjoy the same exemptions from taxation in respect of the
               salaries and emoluments paid to them by the specialized agencies and on the same
               conditions as are enjoyed by officials of the United Nations;

shall be immune from legal process with respect to acts performed
                by them in their official capacity except when the Bank waives this
                immunity;

which discriminates against such obligation or security solely
                because it is guaranteed by the Corporation;
